amily: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万吨，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2.7%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。继续发展和推广优质苎麻新品种，苎麻种植面积达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7.2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.4%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。围绕</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四个一批</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，加快了农业产业化进程，县财政安排专项资金，实施了蔬菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">双百工程</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，支持蔬菜、水产主产区新建扩建冷库</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">处，成功引进了绿丰脱水蔬菜、韩国泡菜等农业产业化龙头企业。大力推进林特山地开发，已落实规划面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，签订山地开发合同面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，完成造林整地面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1.5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩。扎实推进了新农村建设，累计投入建设资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2130</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，重点抓好了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个省级示范村、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个市级示范村的新农村建设试点，官桥八组被评定为</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全国工农业旅游示范点</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。组织实施了三湖连江灌区续建、余码头泵站改造、幸福河流域土地平整、邱家湾农业综合开发低产田改造等农业基础设施工程建设，进一步提高了农业综合抗灾能力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快推进园区建设，招商引资成效显著。按照</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工业新城、城市亮点</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的思路，把建大园区作为重头戏，加快了经济开发区标准化建设。县城投公司充分发挥职能作用，多方筹资融资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6200</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，用于经济开发区和城市基础设施建设。重点实施了工业园道路扩建、土地平整、设施配套等基础工程建设。目前，经济开发区入园落户企业达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">31</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家，比上年增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家；园区规模工业完成产值</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">31.37</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">44.1%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">；上缴入库税金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2983</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">29%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。积极承接东南沿海及武汉城市圈产业转移，启动了与武汉市青山区的走访对接活动，组成了由</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">名县级领导带队的四个招商专班，分赴山东、福建、广东、苏浙沪等沿海地区驻点招商。通过多措并举抓招商，全年共引进项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">48</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，其中投资过亿元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、过千万元项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，合同资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">47.52</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，到位资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9.41</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元，同比增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30.7%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强基础设施建设，城乡面貌明显改观。以全市城市建设现场会在我县召开为契机，加快了城市建设步伐。一年来，全县累计投入资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元，完成了县城建设总体规划修编，先后建成了发展大道改造延伸工程、小新堤路硬化、永丰路硬化配套及樱花路延伸工程，对新区主干道实施了绿化、亮化等综合改造，在新区重要交叉路口新建了现代化</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">交通渠</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，在中心转盘建起了大型电子荧屏，动工兴建了南嘉现代商城、中北家园、江樱花园、水岸星城等一批中高档商贸服务设施和住宅小区。大力改善城乡基础设施，完成了嘉鱼县城至高铁公路改造工程，潘家湾码头已建成并投入使用，陆口大桥已完成投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">700</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万元，完成了武嘉公路复线幸福路改造。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">统筹发展社会事业，社会更加和谐稳定。进一步加强了就业再就业和社会保障工作。全年累计发放小额担保贷款</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">366.8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，帮助</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多名下岗职工走上了自谋职业和自主创业道路；社会保险费征收达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">7229</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，扩面新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6246</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，按时足额发放了离退休职工养老金。城乡社会救助体系更加完善，全年共争取上级各类救助资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2300</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，对困难群众实施了有效救助，累计发放城镇低保金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">976.6</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元；全面启动了农村低保工作，共有</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3501</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">户、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">6505</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人纳入了农村低保对象，累计发放保障金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">153</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。加快了教育事业发展，</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两基</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">成果进一步巩固提高，东方红职校正式招生开学，全县教育教学质量全面提升，教育结构日趋合理。进一步健全了公共卫生医疗及保健体系，完善和规范了新型农村合作医疗制度，县疾控中心已投入使用。大力推进科技、文化、卫生三下乡活动，开展了以弘扬社会主义核心价值观为主题的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">百星耀南嘉</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">评选活动。计划生育出生婴儿性别比下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个单位值。加大了安全生产监管力度，全县安全生产继续保持平稳态势。进一步健全了信访工作机制，在全省率先成立群众工作部，全县信访总量同比下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25.4%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。进一步加强了民主法制和精神文明建设，强化了社会治安综合治理，保持了全县社会安定稳定的良好局面。全县广播电视、新闻出版、民族宗教、外事侨务、残联等事业全面发展；监察、审计、质监、工商、税务等方面工作对经济运行监管作用日益突出；经贸、发改、统计、物价等部门服务经济发展的能力明显增强；人事编制、档案方志、妇女儿童等方面工作全面发展；国防动员、人民防空、民兵预备役工作有了新的进步。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">着力解决民生问题，九件实事全面落实。一年来，我们坚持把改善民生作为工作的出发点和落脚点，倾注真情关心民生，动员各方服务民生，强化举措改善民生，年初县政府承诺为民办好的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件实事全面落实。一是加快推进了经济开发区建设，去年投入开发区建设资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5797</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元。二是全年新增就业岗位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3900</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，帮助下岗失业人员再就业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1600</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人。三是通过多种途径组织城镇下岗失业人员和农民工技能培训</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">9000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人次，组织农村劳动力外出务工</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人。四是投入</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一建三改</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">497</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，完成沼气池建设</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3850</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">口，改厕</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">户，解决了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万人饮水安全问题。五是全年建成通村公路</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">216</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">公里，并完成了嘉鱼至金口一级公路改造的前期准备工作。六是全部免除了农村义务教育阶段学生学杂费，免收了全县义务教育阶段</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">名贫困生书本费。七是全县新型农村合作医疗参合率达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">85%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上。八是全年查螺灭螺面积达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3480</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万平方米，晚血病人救治率达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">100%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">。九是启动了新区文体中心建设，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">80</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元完成了牌洲湾、潘家湾和渡普等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个镇文化站新建和改造工程，投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">多万元新建了</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个村级健身场所和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家农村书屋。在办好九件实事的同时，高度重视人大代表议案、建议和政协委员提案办理工作，全年共办理议案建议</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">35</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件、提案</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">80</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">件。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">总结回顾过去一年的工作，我们倍感欣慰，特别是全县亿元项目增多了，城市街道变亮了，财政收入增长了，农民收入增加了，干部职工增资了。这是全县人民和衷共济、奋力拼搏的结果，我们必须倍加珍惜。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">在肯定成绩的同时，我们也清醒地看到，当前经济和社会发展中还存在一些突出问题和矛盾。一是工业经济总量不大，缺乏大项目，招商引资项目开工率、合同履约率和资金到位率仍然不够理想。二是农业基础依然薄弱，农业产业化程度不高，蔬菜、水产产品单一，名特优品种比重偏低，农产品加工包装滞后，农民持续增收难度较大。三是改善民生的财力偏弱，与人民群众的期望还存在一定的差距。物价上涨压力较大，尤其是对低收入居民生活产生较大影响。四是政府职能和机关作风有待进一步转变，全民创业意识不强，经济发展环境还不够优。对此，我们将高度重视，坚持用改革和发展的办法努力加以解决。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">二、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2008</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年工作的指导思想和主要目标</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2008</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">年是全面贯彻落实党的十七大精神的第一年，是推动科学发展、加快迈入全省第一方阵的关键一年。做好今年的工作，意义十分重大。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2008</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">年政府工作的指导思想是：以党的十七大精神为指导，全面贯彻落实中央、省、市经济工作会议精神，坚持以科学发展观统领经济社会发展全局，继续围绕</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">建大园区、招大项目、办大工业、搞大服务</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的发展思路，着力推进产业优化升级，着力推进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两型社会</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建设，着力推进民生改善，努力实现全县经济社会又好又快发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">今年经济社会发展的主要预期目标是</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五增两降一进位</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，即：全县生产总值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上，全社会固定资产投资增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上，财政收入增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上，其中国税、地税实现双过亿，规模以上工业增加值增长</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">25%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上，农民人均纯收入增加</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">元以上；全社会</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">GDP</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">能耗下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2%</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">以上，工业污染排放量下降</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5%</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">以上；力争县域经济综合实力在全省排序前进一位。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">根据上述指导思想和目标，做好今年政府工作，必须深入贯彻落实科学发展观，更加注重转变发展方式，坚持好字优先，好中求快、优中求进，努力推动经济又好又快发展；更加注重体制机制创新和自主创新，坚持开放先导、创新驱动，努力在招商引资和项目建设上实现新突破；更加注重统筹城乡发展，大力发展现代农业，扎实推进社会主义新农村建设；更加注重社会建设，坚持以人为本，认真解决关系人民群众切身利益的突出问题，努力在改善民生上有更大作为；更加注重生态文明建设，坚持节约资源、保护环境，推进节能减排，大力发展循环经济；更加注重政府自身建设，坚持求真务实、真抓实干，切实提高政府推动科学发展的能力和水平，不断开创全县各项工作的新局面。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">三、努力促进全县经济社会又好又快发展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">办好嘉鱼的事，关键是要深入贯彻落实科学发展观，切实转变经济发展方式，重点在产业升级、结构优化、科技创新、城乡协调发展等方面实现新的突破，着力提高发展质量和效益，努力促进全县经济社会又好又快发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（一）加快推进新型工业化，着力培育新的经济增长点</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工业化始终是全县经济工作的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">牛鼻子</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">。今年，我们要立足现有工业基础和资源优势，培植壮大骨干企业，加快重点项目建设，构建优势产业集群，增强县域经济发展实力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">做大做强优势产业。围绕纺织、矿产、化工、建材和加工制造等五大支柱产业，加大对骨干企业的扶持力度，促进企业产品向上下游延伸。围绕牌洲湾油气田开发，争取国家和省市支持，重点规划建设天然气产业园区，精心策划推介天然气产业链招商项目，新办多家化工企业。依托田野集团</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">博士后科研工作站</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，积极发展高新技术产业。发挥纺织产业优势，延伸发展针织、制衣、床上用品等配套产业链条，进一步扩大纺织产业规模。通过做强优势产业，力争在全县新增一批销售过亿元、税收过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元的骨干企业，全年新增规模企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家以上。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">着力抓好项目建设。项目建设是县域经济发展的载体，更是一项贯穿全年的中心工作。今年要全力抓好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">16</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个重点项目建设，力争完成投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元以上，建成投产项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上。其中，中石特种钢管二期工程、元阳食品二期工程要尽快建成投产；在建项目中，山湖温泉要在今年底开园营业，牌洲湾石油天然气进入实质性开发，高强锰业、金嘉木业、瑞克电动车等要在今年建成投产；加大葛洲坝水泥、比伦生活日用纸、天洋塑木新材料、盛宇印染二期、洁丽雅纺织二期、德茂环保设备、方圆船舶、莱福特生物制药等</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个在建或拟建项目的协调服务力度，力争年底前有</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个项目建成投产。同时，要积极谋划一批投资规模大、产业链长、事关长远发展的建设项目，确保项目有序接替。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全力推进园区开发。继续按照政策向园区倾斜、财力向园区集中、产业向园区集聚的思路，标准化建设经济开发区，提高园区的吸引力和承载力。今年再投入资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万元以上，重点完成园区主干道刷黑和一路二路土方工程建设，做好园区内民房拆迁工作，建设开发区企业孵化服务大楼，加快园区配套设施建设，抓紧做好嘉鱼经济开发区整体发展和建设规划，建成县城至官桥八组一体化十里工业长廊，真正把经济开发区建成工业新城、城市亮点。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力培育精品名牌。充分运用政策引导、项目扶持、资金支持等手段，帮助企业加大技改投入，实施技术改造，提高生产效益。加快推进质量兴县、品牌立县战略，巩固现有品牌，培育精品名牌，今年要力争新创中国名牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、国家免检产品</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个、省级名牌</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">个。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（二）加快推进现代农业，建设社会主义新农村</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">从当前农村发展的实际来看，要更加重视巩固农业基础，重点在构建特色产业体系、推动农业科技创新、加快农业产业化经营上做文章，扎实推进现代农业发展和新农村建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">调整优化农业结构。我县农业在经受这次罕见的低温雨雪冰冻灾害后，调整优化农业结构、提高抗御风险能力已经刻不容缓。今年，我们要下大力气解决蔬菜、水产、粮食、苎麻等产业种植模式落后和品种结构单一的问题，大力发展规模农业、特色农业、品牌农业和效益农业。继续围绕</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">四个一批</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，发展壮大蔬菜、水产产业，着力构建特色农业产业体系，加快推进蔬菜板块建设，扩大精细蔬菜种植面积，加快潘家湾蔬菜大市场等项目建设，组建蔬菜配送公司，大力发展名特优水产品，加快健康养殖小区建设，今年要力争</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上蔬菜品种获得国家绿色认证，引进蔬菜新品种</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">50</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，争创全省水产十强县。加快山地开发，认真贯彻落实市委、市政府</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">在山上再造一个咸宁</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">战略，按照</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五线三区</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的总体规划要求，加大荒山开发和低产低效林改造力度，加快高产高效林和特色产业基地建设，重点发展优质水果、花卉苗木、有机茶叶及速生丰产竹类、意杨、泡桐等林特产业，力争全年新增山地开发面积</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万亩。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">深入推进农业产业化。积极扶持农产品加工企业快速发展，重点支持世天、山绿、国美、嘉台双美、牌洲湾食品等企业发展壮大。充分发挥农业资源优势，大力开展农产品加工项目招商，今年要力争引进</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家规模以上蔬菜、水产加工企业，新增市级龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，新增省级龙头企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家。加强品牌建设，充分放大</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">牌洲湾</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">螃蟹、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">联乐</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">蔬菜、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">田野</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">瓜果和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">潘家湾</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">地理性标识等品牌效应，提升农产品知名度和市场竞争力。积极发展专业合作经济组织，进一步健全农产品销售网络，完善流通体系，推进特色农业发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">积极推动农业技术创新。加快引进农业科技成果，提高农产品科技含量。充分发挥潘家湾、茅洲垴两个农业科技示范园的作用，带动周边村组发展高效农业。切实抓好适用技术的推广应用，水稻轻简高效综合配套技术推广应用面积要达到</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万亩，扩大农作物测土配方施肥技术推广面积，继续抓好蔬菜</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">双百</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工程，建立</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三安</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">示范基地</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亩。加快农产品标准化生产步伐，建立健全农产品质量标准体系、安全监测体系和动植物疫病防治体系。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快推进新农村建设。认真落实强农惠农政策，切实做好粮食直补、良种补贴、退耕还林补助、农机补贴、能繁母猪补贴、农资综合直补等资金管理发放工作，探索良种补贴与良种推广有机结合的有效形式。以改善农村基础设施为重点，进一步提高公共财政涉农资金比例，不断增加对农业农村的投入，全面推动社会主义新农村建设。今年要按照新农村建设总体规划，扩大新农村建设试点范围，组织开展以村容整洁为重点的农村</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">清洁家园</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">行动。加强农村安全饮水、乡村道路、电网、沼气和通讯信息服务平台建设，突出抓好高产农田建设、病险水库除险加固、百里长渠整治以及大中型排灌设施的更新改造，进一步改善农村生产生活条件。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（三）加快推进开放先导战略，以大开放促进大发展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全方位推进招商引资。要紧紧抓住东部沿海地区产业加快向内地转移和武汉城市圈</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两型社会</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">试验区建设的机遇，主动承接国内外特别是</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">长珠闽</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">等沿海地区产业转移，加快推进与武汉城市圈在观念、体制、产业、市场、基础设施、环境保护和生态建设等方面的全面对接，充分整合优势资源，包装一批优势项目，力争引进一批高新技术产业项目和劳动密集型项目，重点引进农产品加工、纺织服装、精细化工、电子信息等企业。今年，全县要力争新引进项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">45</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，其中亿元投资项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，到位固定资产投资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">亿元以上。要不断探索与创新招商思路和招商方法，重点抓好委托代理招商、产业链招商和以商招商。今年，全县将选派</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">名局级干部外出招商，按照工作经费与招商业绩挂钩、跟踪考核与奖惩兑现相结合的方式，明确招商区域，强化招商责任，提高招商实效。继续实行招商引资项目跟踪服务机制，加大对签约项目和在谈项目的跟踪服务力度，切实提高项目的合同履约率、资金到位率和投产率，增强经济发展后劲。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快发展开放型经济。转变外贸发展方式，优化出口商品结构，加强出口基地建设，扩大医用纺织、棉麻加工、服装、皮革皮件等传统产品出口，加快推进蔬菜、水产等农产品加工出口，支持高新技术产品出口，提高出口产品质量、规模和档次。力争今年引进外资项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个以上，实现外贸出口</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万美元以上，新增有自营出口权企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力推动全民创业。在全社会大力营造</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">崇尚成功、鼓励创业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的人文环境，充分调动广大群众参与创业、大胆探索、敢闯敢试的积极性。制定鼓励全民创业的政策措施，搭建全民创业平台</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">支持科技人员离岗创业、机关干部下海创业、大中专毕业生自主创业、外出务工人员回乡创业，激发全民创业热情。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（四）加快推进现代服务业，提升第三产业发展水平</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快发展旅游产业。充分发挥旅游业带动作用，突破性发展温泉休闲、农业观光等相关旅游产业，重点抓好山湖温泉度假村项目建设，努力将山湖温泉度假村打造成华中地区一流的温泉休闲旅游景点。依托潘家湾蔬菜产业资源，鼓励民间创办农业观光旅游基地，加快发展以农家乐为重点的农业观光旅游产业。充分发挥官桥八组新农村建设的知名度和影响力，大力发展政务和商务考察参观产业。加强与武汉及周边城市的旅游合作，联手创建圈内无障碍旅游区，着力打造武汉后花园。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">积极发展商贸流通业。大力发展物流服务产业，以服务园区企业为目的，推进物流园区建设。加快发展金融、保险、通讯、计算机服务、中介服务、法律咨询等新兴产业；围绕现代工业、现代农业，大力发展产品设计、研究开发、市场营销等生产性服务业，形成工业、农业、服务业联动发展、相互促进的格局。继续抓好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工业品下乡、农产品进城</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">，逐步构建起农村现代化流通网络。稳步发展房地产业，规范房地产市场秩序。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加大市场监管力度。强化产品质量和食品安全监管，重点加强对群众日常生活必需品的监督管理力度，集中开展各种专项检查和整治活动。大力推进食品安全信用体系建设，重点在食品生产、市场流通、餐饮服务等行业推行企业诚信体系建设，从源头上有效遏制食品安全隐患。加强药品安全管理，规范农村药品市场秩序，创建农村药品</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两网</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建设省级示范县。切实保持市场物价平稳，进一步健全价格监控和预警机制，妥善做好涉及民生的原材料、燃料、农资、食品、医药等价格调控工作，加强涉农价费、中介服务等收费管理，努力使价费水平保持在社会可承受的范围。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（五）加快推进节能减排，积极转变经济发展方式</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加快科技创新步伐。要把科技创新作为转变经济发展方式的中心环节，大力推进企业自主创新，建立以企业为主体、市场为导向、产学研相结合的技术创新体系。积极推进科技创新平台建设，鼓励有条件的企业建立研究中心和重点实验室，加大对企业技改项目的支持力度，力争今年实施科技攻关项目</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个，申请专利</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">件，培育高新技术产品</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项，发展高新技术企业</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家以上，企业投入技改资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4.1</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">亿元，努力提高科技对经济发展的贡献率。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">深入推进节能减排。要加快建立科学的节能减排指标体系和监督考核体系，严格落实各项节能减排措施。按照国家产业政策，在关闭现有</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家小造纸企业的基础上，对排污不达标、规模及技术指标达不到要求的</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五小</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">企业，特别是小化工等企业全部予以关停，对能耗高、污染重、技术落后的工艺实施强制性淘汰。按照</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">治旧控新、建管并举</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">的原则，建立健全严格的准入制度，严格控制新上高耗能、高污染项目。定期对重点用能单位的能源利用情况进行监督检查，支持耗能大户实施技术改造，积极推广治污新技术和节能实用技术，降低工业废气物的排放。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建好重点生态工程。加强重点流域区域水资源保护和水污染治理，加快桑德污水处理厂建设，对工业园区工业废水和城区生活污水进行集中处理。积极支持盛宇印染车间整体迁建工业园区，着手规划风华化工、兴宁化工、嘉能热电等企业整体搬迁，并做好搬迁前期准备工作。大力推进以沼气池建设为龙头的农村生态循环经济建设，推广农业生态种养模式，走出一条资源共生、良性互动的生态循环经济发展路子。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（六）加快推进财源建设，切实做好财税金融工作</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强税源体系建设。财政是经济的综合反映，近年来，我县财政收入快速增长，收支矛盾有了明显缓解，但财政困难仍然是经济社会发展中的突出问题。必须切实加强财源建设，突出强工业、活三产，建立多元化、后劲足的财源体系，夯实财政增收基础，千方百计做大财政蛋糕。要对现有税源状况进行一次全面摸底调查，跟踪服务，积极扶持，确保现有税源继续保持在一个稳定增长的水平上。要重点培植支柱税源，特别是要加强对纳税大户的培育，拿出硬措施帮助企业解决生产经营过程中的困难和问题，力争在五大支柱产业中，每个产业培育</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">家年税收过</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万元的龙头企业。要积极开辟新兴税源，大力发展农产品和矿产加工企业，积极发展文化体育产业、信息服务业、旅游业、房地产业等，为税源建设开辟新的途径。要强化征管手段，减少税源流失，确保应收尽收，颗粒归仓。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">完善财政支出管理。突出财政的公共服务职能，坚持依法理财、科学理财，强化支出管理，大力压缩一般性支出，集中财力保重点、办实事，加大对教育、卫生、科技、文化、就业再就业、社会保障、节能减排等方面的投入，积极探索有效的财政保障方式，努力构建改善民生的长效机制。积极争取国债资金和上级转移支付资金，规范财政性资金使用监督管理和投资项目管理，不断提高财政资金的使用效益。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">强化金融服务功能。大力支持金融部门的工作，进一步健全政府部门、银行和企业协调沟通制度，搭建银企合作平台，有效破解存贷差持续拉大的问题。切实加大对优势资源开发、工业项目、新农村建设和基础设施等重点领域的支持力度，增加信贷投入，更好地发挥金融对地方经济发展的支持和保障作用。要加大</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">招行引资</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">力度，争取各类商业银行在我县设立分支机构。认真做好中小企业信用担保工作，有效缓解中小企业贷款难问题。要加大信用镇建设力度，切实解决到期贷款回收率偏低、不良贷款占比过高的现状，进一步巩固</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">最佳金融信用县</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">创建成果。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（七）加快推进基础设施建设，进一步改善城乡面貌</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强生态宜居城市建设。按照</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">重点建设新城区，改造提升老城区</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的原则，高起点、高标准推进城市建设，大力开展省级园林城市创建活动，积极争创第二届湖北省城市规划建设管理</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">楚天杯</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">，努力把县城建设成为最佳宜居的山水园林城市。加强城市基础设施建设，重点抓好城区主干道刷黑、樱花路工业园段、小湖路、永丰路至南嘉大道段等道路工程建设，加快推进电力小区、嘉和明园和文化艺术中心建设，进一步完善城市功能，拓展城市发展空间。强化城市管理，重点规范公汽管理，加强对夜市摊点、沙滩浴场和农贸市场周边环境秩序的整治，抓好社区垃圾清扫清运和垃圾池的定点建设。加强城市绿化建设，突出植物造景和园林文化两大重点，重点抓好人民公园、滨湖景观带工程建设，努力形成以人民广场绿化建设为中心，以道路绿化为主线，机关单位、小区和庭院绿化联片成网的新景象。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快交通基础设施建设。加强城乡路网建设，尽快动工兴建嘉鱼至金口一级公路改造工程，抓好咸合线、京珠连接线等二级公路维护和保养。加快推进陆口大桥建设，力争完成水上桥面工程建设，尽快打通嘉鱼至赤壁旅游黄金通道。启动潘家湾码头二期扩建工程，进一步提升码头吞吐能力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快城乡一体化进程。坚持以工促农、以城带乡，统筹城乡基础设施、公共服务、劳动就业和社会管理等事业发展，缩小城乡差距，进一步提高城镇化水平。加快小城镇建设步伐，重点推进省市级重点镇建设，着力抓好集镇街道环境整治、基础设施改造，不断提升小城镇建设品位。大力发展镇级经济，吸引更多农民向小城镇集中。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（八）加快推进社会事业发展，共建共享和谐嘉鱼</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">切实加强就业和社会保障工作。坚持以创业带就业，努力形成自主创业、自谋职业和灵活就业等多渠道就业新格局。实施积极的就业政策，完善小额贷款担保工作机制，扩大放贷规模，推进城镇新增劳动力就业和下岗失业人员再就业。进一步完善社会保障体系，依法推进基本养老、基本医疗、失业、工伤、生育保险扩面征缴，力争扩面新增</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">15000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">人次。进一步健全完善城乡社会救助体系，积极推进惠民医院建设和城市老年公寓建设，建立健全农村低保和养老保险制度，不断完善城乡困难群众大病医疗、城乡孤儿、农村五保、慈善捐赠等专业救助制度，进一步巩固提高最低生活保障和医疗保障水平。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">加强民主法制和精神文明建设。切实加强农村基层组织建设，提高基层群众自我管理、自我服务、自我教育、自我监督的能力和水平。强化村级财务管理，严禁少数村委会违规变卖资产、私自发包等行为。积极开展</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">五五</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">普法教育，加强法制建设，全面推进地方、行业、基层依法治理。深化收入分配制度改革，加强对收入分配的宏观调节，建立企业职工工资正常增长和足额支付的保障机制。依法保障人民在政治、文化、经济、社会等方面的权益，促进社会公平。认真实施《劳动合同法》等劳动法律法规，加强劳动保障监督执法和劳动争议仲裁工作</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">切实维护职工合法权益</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">,</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">建立和谐劳动关系。深入开展社会主义荣辱观和公民道德教育，推进社会主义精神文明建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">大力发展各项社会事业。优先发展教育事业，进一步完善义务教育经费保障机制。加快农村中小学寄宿制学校建设，全力提高办学质量和办学水平，促进教育公平。整合职业教育资源，积极支持东方红等职业技术学校发展壮大。推进文化创新，大力发展公益性文化事业，广泛开展以</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">全民健身与奥运同行</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">为主题的系列群众体育活动，丰富群众文化生活。加强公共卫生基础设施和服务体系建设，启动县人民医院整体迁建工程，完善农村三级卫生服务网络，发展社区卫生服务。做好血吸虫病、艾滋病、结核病等防治工作。更加注重人口和计划生育工作，坚持人口和计划生育目标管理责任制不动摇，坚持</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一票否决</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">不动摇，严格实行计划生育包保责任制，继续对计划生育工作出现严重问题的地方和部门设立重点管理</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">笼子</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">，进一步加大</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">两清一治</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">工作力度，严厉打击非法鉴定胎儿性别和非法中止妊娠的行为，依法征收计划外生育社会抚养费，进一步提高计划生育服务和管理水平，坚决遏制计划外生育反弹，稳定低生育水平。高度重视环境保护，严格落实新建项目环评和</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">三同时</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">制度，从源头上有效防治污染。切实加强国土资源管理，严格保护耕地，促进节约集约用地。加强社会治安综合治理，巩固</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">平安嘉鱼</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">创建成果。强化安全生产责任制，加强对交通运输、工矿企业、建筑施工等领域的安全管理，坚决遏制重特大安全事故发生。切实做好信访工作，畅通群众合理诉求渠道，依法及时处理群众信访问题。加强社区建设管理，广泛开展和谐社区创建活动，建设管理有序、服务完善、文明祥和的新型社区。注重发展残疾人事业，支持妇女、儿童、老龄事业发展。进一步加强国防教育、国防动员、民兵预备役和人防工作，做好军转干部、复员退伍军人优抚安置工作。做好民族宗教、外事侨务、气象地震、档案方志等工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">四、加强政府自身建设</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">面对新形势新任务，政府及政府各部门必须要按照科学执政、民主执政、依法执政的要求，着力加强自身建设，努力提高行政能力和管理水平，不辜负人民的期望。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（一）加快转变政府职能。要进一步深化行政管理体制改革，推动制度和管理创新，坚持把转变政府职能作为做好各项工作的基本途径。要在履行好经济调节和市场监管职能的同时，更加注重强化社会管理和公共服务职能，特别是要进一步健全各种突发事件和自然灾害应急机制，提高政府应对公共危机的能力。要继续完善公众参与、专家论证和政府决策相结合的决策机制，提高科学决策的水平。政府所有重大决策，都要在深入调查研究、广泛听取意见、充分进行论证的基础上，由集体研究决定。这将作为一项基本工作制度长期坚持下去。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（二）全面推进依法行政。政府及政府各部门要严格按照法定权限和程序行使权力、履行职责，所有政府工作人员都要学会并善于依法处理经济社会事务。政府的一切权力都是人民赋予的，必须对人民负责，接受人民监督。要自觉接受县人大及其常委会的法律监督，接受县政协的民主监督。认真办理人大代表议案、建议和政协委员提案，诚恳听取党外人士和各人民团体的意见，接受新闻舆论和社会公众监督，确保权力在阳光下运行。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">（三）加强政府效能建设。牢固树立</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">服务第一</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">的观念，让职责、权力服从服务于发展的需要，让规定、程序服从服务于效率的需要，让评价、结论服从服务于最后的成果业绩。继续做好行政审批制度改革工作，健全行政服务中心运作机制，加强服务经济社会载体建设，努力为企业提供</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">保姆式</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">服务。推行电子政务，优化政府管理流程，提高办事效率。加大政务公开力度，继续完善信息公开、承诺服务等制度。完善目标管理考核体系，推进政府绩效管理。严格执行行政问责制，严肃查处</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">不作为</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">、</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">乱作为</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">、失职渎职行为，着力提高政府执行力，确保政令畅通。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">（四）推进政府廉政建设。认真落实廉政建设责任制，健全完善教育、制度、监督并重的惩治和预防腐败体系，健全领导干部经济责任审计和离任审计制度，坚持从源头上治理腐败，坚决纠正损害群众利益的各种不正之风，从严惩治商业贿赂等腐败行为。对政府工作人员要严格要求、严格教育、严格监督，全体政府工作人员特别是领导干部，都要始终保持谦虚谨慎、不骄不躁、艰苦奋斗的作风，恪尽职守，勤奋工作，公道正派，乐于奉献。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">各位代表，民生连民心，民心关乎和谐。今年，我们将继续为人民群众办好</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">10</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">件实事，让改革开放和经济社会发展成果惠及全县人民。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">①</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">新增城镇就业</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，帮助</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1500</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">名下岗失业人员实现再就业；完成农民工转岗培训</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">人，新增转移农村劳动力</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3000</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">人。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">②</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">完善城市廉租住房制度，向城市低收入家庭发放住房租赁补贴，解决县城区所有人均住房面积在</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">平方米以下最低收入家庭的住房困难；积极向上争取资金</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">120</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">万元，实施</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">福彩安居工程</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">，帮助农村特困户进行危房改造。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">③</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">从今年春季起免除全县义务教育阶段学生学杂费和教科书费，全面启动</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">20</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">所农村中小学寄宿制学校标准化建设。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">④</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">一建三改</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">项目建设，新建沼气池</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">5000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">口，改厕</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2000</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">户，再解决</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">万人饮水安全问题。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑤</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快医疗卫生和文化基础设施建设，完成</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">30</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">个村卫生室标准化建设，建成</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">农家书屋</font></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&rdquo;10</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">家。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑥</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">新增农村低保对象</span></font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1675</span><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">人，推进城市低保对象医疗保险改革试点工作，将城市低保对象全部纳入医疗保险范围。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑦</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">动工兴建污水处理厂。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑧</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">完成茶庵新区农贸市场主体工程建设。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑨</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">启动三湖假日大酒店至山湖温泉的滨湖景观带工程建设，按期保质保量抓好人民公园建设。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">⑩</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">加快交通基础设施建设，完成发展大道刷黑工程，动工兴建嘉鱼至金口一级公路，完成全县通村公路建设。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial\\\\\">各位代表，当前嘉鱼经济社会发展势头良好，今年的各项工作任务更为繁重。让我们在县委的坚强领导下，在县人大、县政协的监督支持下，紧紧依靠全县人民，同心同德，锐意进取，扎实工作，共同谱写嘉鱼发展的新篇章！</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: Arial; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>');");
